CrewMember - Class in main
 
CrewMember(String, String) - Constructor for class main.CrewMember
This function constructs a crew member with a name and a type
There are six different types to choose from each with different skills:
–Superhuman: Default health of 120%
–Hunger Buster: Hunger rate is 5%
–Fresher: Tiredness rate is 5%
–Builder: Repair rate is 15%
–Immune: Unaffected by the space plague
–Terminator: Ability to prevent alien pirates from stealing items, but takes 10% damage in doing so
